item.title: Rooms
item.dc:creator: Yingying Zhang
item.content:encoded:
Cake & Bread

We insist on using natural cream from New Zealand, and also adhere to the art of both beauty and texture. The purchased raw materials will be personally selected and processed by us to eliminate bad ingredients.

Cake

Compared to the monotonous taste of many cake embryos, each of our cakes must be baked with raw materials, and the richness of taste buds is a guarantee of our good reputation.

Frozen cheese cake

It is a non baking cake that adds a coagulant to the cheesecake and then refrigerates until the cake solidifies.

Angel Food Cake

Angel cake does not add a drop of fat, and even the egg yolk containing fat is removed, which is very healthy.

Pound Cake

Unlike regular cakes that are soft, pound cakes have a more solid texture. The taste is very mellow.

Black Forest Cake

It blends the sourness of cherries, the sweetness of cream, the bitterness of chocolate, and the mellow aroma of cherry wine.

Bread

The freshly baked bread has a comprehensive color, aroma, and mellow taste, with a fragrant and soft texture that can withstand the scrutiny of various flavors.

Brioche

French traditional bread, with a large oil content, golden and crisp skin and super soft interior, is often eaten as a Dim sum.

Danish Pastry

Using more traditional production methods, the flavors are original croissants and chocolate buns.

Natural Fermented Bread

Our store uses natural enzymes made from fruits, grains, etc. to make different types of bread.

Sandwich Meal Bag

Using multiple ingredients to enrich the possibility of bread and the layering of flavors.
